About:
This app does cool things and great stuff.
Sometimes it completes exceptional actions.

Use:
Jam on the buttons with your marshmallow pig fingers.

To install the JSON parser:
Download JSON_2.1.1.dmg from 
Copy the content of the 'SDKs' folder to ~/Library/SDKs. (You may have to create that directory.)
In the target build options, add (This should already be there)
Additional SDKs
$HOME/Library/SDKs/JSON/$(PLATFORM_NAME).sdk
Other Linker Flags
-ObjC -ljson
Code Signing Resource Rules Path
$(SDKROOT)/ResourceRules.plist

To install the TouchXML parser: (This should already be there)
The build files for TouchXML are included in the project
In the target build options, add
Other Linker Flags
-lxml2
Header Search Paths
/usr/include/libxml2

